sentences: She has collaborated with several international acts and is currently working on her debut album, citing influences from such artists as Phil Collins, Shirley Bassey, Sting, David Bowie, Machel Montano and Sparrow, a Trinidadian Calypsonian.
She is also a former member of the 1990s girl group 7669.
They released one studio album - 1993's 7669 East from a Bad Block.
